Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.60,0:00:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人世谓缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系结的丝线纠结缠绕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱可悲的彼岸花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.00,0:00:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在愤怒 悲伤 泪水中度日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.50,0:00:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午夜零点的帷幕彼方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.20,0:00:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难消之恨 愿为消之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.97,0:00:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;20;0;20,{\fs18\an8}本字幕由漫游字幕组制作。翻译：Chris 校对：大神 其他杂项：狒狒。勿将此用于商业，有爱支持正版。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上加藤老师捐的两万元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.50,0:00:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捐款总数达到了十万元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.00,0:00:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捐款交给班长桥本真由美保管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.00,0:00:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会负责保管好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.00,0:00:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.60,0:01:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 我明明好好放在包里的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.70,0:01:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 桥本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑 黑田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.50,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}来自黄昏的彼方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.10,0:01:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 可是十万啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.90,0:01:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊 是募捐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.90,0:01:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么都是全班…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.60,0:01:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.70,0:01:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也没发生募捐的钱也顺利送到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是托谁的福 你应该清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 钱呢 带来了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.00,0:01:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下借你的全还清了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前还的只是利息哦 利息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么怨言么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.00,0:02:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有我借给你的话会怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讨厌的话就告诉大家好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我保管的钱弄丢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点口渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买果汁来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.30,0:02:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你知道地狱通信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午夜零点在主页上写入内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什么仇怨恨都能帮你报的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.00,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个补习班的朋友的朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说试过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个好像非常危险啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托的人自己也会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还听说有人突然就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.60,0:03:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是碳酸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你一直很讨厌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就要喝碳酸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.00,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.30,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4x-2x=2x
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此2x=120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后除以2 x就等于60
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.00,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了x的值后 把x代入一开始的式子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,700)}放学后 老地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.30,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,y的值也就能算出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.10,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近家里常常会丢钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然金额很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是家里没人时有小偷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说最近很多同样的家也被偷了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸晚归的时候就我们两个女人在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是报警…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(420,200)\fad(300,0)\frz-8\t(400,1100,1,\frz0)}君之怨恨    愿为消之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委托的人自己也会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 桥本同学她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说晚上在繁华街看到她了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你渴不渴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴了 渴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去自动售货机买吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是个正经的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表一点都看不出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 被听到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.00,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥本同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加藤老师叫你去办公室一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到一个奇怪的传言啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你夜晚在外面游荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得肯定是毫无根据的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.60,0:06:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是这样的孩子 我再清楚不过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.60,0:07:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 你的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么什么都不告诉我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近你好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不愿意这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道最近家里不见的钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈是相信你的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}现在是12点，指7的是定闹表的指针。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(420,200)}君之怨恨    愿为消之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已予受理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.70,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊 那只眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.00,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚8点 别忘了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后 什么都没发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.00,0:08:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果 什么地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搭讪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是能请客吃饭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是大叔也没关系哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪你没本事拿钱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在发什么呆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数会上钩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.20,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是要拉客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.90,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.60,0:09:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK 你一个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去呢 要吃什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么逃走了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再忘记钱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.20,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你这张双人照公开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.70,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呼唤我来的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.00,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.00,0:12:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法前往极乐净土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将饱尝痛楚与苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远徘徊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听吗 真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你谈谈么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.00,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才 学校收到了邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.80,0:14:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要辩解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的人的确是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得羞耻吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为中学生竟然做成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还很相信你 可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.90,0:14:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.70,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 希望请你的父母明天来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.30,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去明年的高中保送也会变的很困难吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.00,0:15:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14\pos(455,240)\frz-6}10点\N\N\N\N到学校\N\N\N知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真磨蹭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.90,0:16:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美 你在哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊 你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美 难道你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.10,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.00,0:17:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.80,0:17:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到底怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起来也是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.30,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我不大喜欢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 在做白日梦吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 捡个球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个没用的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得教训教训她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.90,0:18:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.20,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么回事 学校好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道了 这边来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.00,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 老师 去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.30,0:18:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 朋友们都在等着你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚矢 救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚矢 亚矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你偷的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊 这完全是胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么证据么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有谁看到了么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 有点铭记于心了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是真由美的同伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然做出这么过分的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还说我们做得过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.00,0:20:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不承认自己的罪行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.00,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 不要这么倔强哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.80,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是戏弄了她一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.30,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是闹着玩的 闹着玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.00,0:20:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没做什么坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这么说哦 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.00,0:21:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等这是哪 要带我去哪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.00,0:22:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由美 加藤老师在叫你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.60,0:22:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说想跟你谈谈准备运动会的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.60,0:22:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.90,0:22:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神好多了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.60,0:22:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有段时间眼睛都是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.00,0:22:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.00,0:22:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个状态 实行委员要加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.20,0:22:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死后 灵魂亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.40,0:23:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
